  "text": "All PFV Gag packaging constructs used in this study are based on the parental pcoPG4 vector or its Cterminal EYFP tagged variant pcoPG4 CeYFP [CITATION_1] . The PFV Gag packaging constructs used in this study are depicted in Figure 1A . The packaging constructs encoding mutant Gag protein with deletion in individual GR boxes (pcoPG4 ΔGRI, pcoPG4 ΔGRII, pcoPG4 ΔGRIII) have been described previously [CITATION_2] . Two additional PFV Gag packaging constructs were generated for this study. The ΔGR mutant (pcoPG4 ΔGR, pcoPG4 CeYFP ΔGR) has all three GR boxes simultaneously deleted and each replaced by a TGAS peptide sequences as found in the original individual GR box deletion mutants [CITATION_3] . In the GR R/A mutant (pcoPG4 GR R/A, pcoPG4 CeYFP GR R/A) 23 arginine residues between aa 485 and 614 of PFV Gag were replaced by alanine.",
